{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:30.844221+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 6c708c510171c17fee8c35ed6c39e513620500b8)", "id": "lc_6d7f1f0f-1f22-4f4d-a8f4-f0102e9cfdf0"}, {"type": "text", "text": "CREATE INDEX idx_sessions_user_id ON sessions(user_id);\n", "id": "lc_bb3e6ab6-b7b7-44ec-8658-235e1285fd60"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "6612cbfd-5998-4986-8414-8149f72e2f21", "tool_call_id": "call_03_gp6Vn70hRuJbsYXYY4Sp6905", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:30.862988+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 9a7ab4a43b359ce089e5b88c4f6f7515daa7431c)", "id": "lc_6314de7b-0f88-40b0-962f-ae3430341441"}, {"type": "text", "text": "CREATE TABLE sessions (\n    id          UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    user_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n    issued_at   TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),\n    expires_at  TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n);\n", "id": "lc_a0e48b22-6eb3-4d77-9147-047463246ddd"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "8881a13a-0b29-49bc-8cdf-70da52d6b24a", "tool_call_id": "call_02_cUD9ywNwZL0ZgJKJAFYt1811", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:30.877366+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 04c0f5484ad13de523e75568ae9be6c1f7f2152d)", "id": "lc_0c4a22a7-9eb1-45b5-adea-ee48d4bd16ac"}, {"type": "text", "text": "CREATE TABLE users (\n    id           BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n    email        TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n    display_name TEXT,\n    created_at   TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n", "id": "lc_8cba24d7-8f3e-489e-a5ec-784261e29034"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "2b99fe43-2efd-41e4-bcf3-969fbdd269aa", "tool_call_id": "call_01_SuHWQoj1fq2J04W5khSp3028", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:30.883488+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 890470cbcd8b22c382d09c9d7ffd222ed613ce36)", "id": "lc_8221c320-a6be-418f-9d98-03f0d24d0d92"}, {"type": "text", "text": "#!/usr/bin/env bash\n# Apply all SQL files under migrations/ to the running pgdev container.\n# Order: filename glob, lexicographic.\nset -euo pipefail\n\nCONTAINER=\"${PGDEV_CONTAINER:-pgdev_db}\"\nDB_USER=\"${POSTGRES_USER:-app}\"\nDB_NAME=\"${POSTGRES_DB:-app}\"\n\n# Note: relies on shell glob expansion ordering, not on `find`.\n# Tested on bash and zsh with default LC_COLLATE.\nfor f in migrations/*.sql; do\n    echo \"Applying $f\"\n    docker exec -i \"$CONTAINER\" psql -U \"$DB_USER\" -d \"$DB_NAME\" < \"$f\"\ndone\n", "id": "lc_62aca05c-aabd-49d0-b99c-2d0c033fe299"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "aec458d9-be9c-4941-9de6-4cc00035b8d2", "tool_call_id": "call_04_hBryPXLbFI55ibaQv2H93134", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:30.888459+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 919f9c0b246a5df3ca8f359645ea21596c7584e5)", "id": "lc_09432ce9-2174-4523-8b7a-88a37d85d881"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# Migration History\n\nA chronological record of all migrations that have been applied in any\ndeployed environment of this database. Kept here for audit / on-call\nreference. Migration files themselves live in `migrations/`; this file\nrecords *what was run when*, not what is currently checked in.\n\n| Date       | File                                | Notes                                              |\n|------------|-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|\n| 2024-11-04 | `001_create_users.sql`              | Initial users table.                               |\n| 2024-12-10 | `002_create_sessions.sql`           | sessions + FK.                                     |\n| 2025-01-22 | `003_add_session_index.sql`         | Index on sessions.user_id.                         |\n| 2025-02-18 | `004_partition_users.sql`           | Range partition users by created_at (monthly).     |\n| 2025-03-05 | `005_archive_legacy_sessions.sql`   | Move >90d sessions to sessions_archive.            |\n| 2025-04-12 | `006_grant_readonly_role.sql`       | Create app_readonly role + grants.                 |\n\nThis file is updated as part of each deploy. The `migrations/` directory\nmay temporarily not contain entries listed here if they have been\narchived to `migrations/archived/`; the history above is authoritative\nfor \"what has run\".\n", "id": "lc_5384bc91-436d-49a3-8ce6-86ae70700b5d"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "d774ed90-d612-42f1-bfce-0330606da24d", "tool_call_id": "call_00_wzIx0JPxhuErLBrDEG211995", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
